docs.title: 🎨 Open Symbols
docs.text: Welcome to the Unicode Open Symbols!   Browse through curated pages of open-use decorative, pictographic, and symbolic Unicode characters, sorted by their official block.

docs.title: 🔎 Categories
docs.text: → Arrows ★ Misc Symbols ✦ Dingbats ⬜ Geometric Shapes ∑ Math Symbols ⚙ Misc. Technical 🎭 Pictographs

docs.title: ⬛ Geometric Shapes & Blocks
docs.text: Covers multiple related ranges: - Box Drawing: U+2500–U+257F - Block Elements: U+2580–U+259F - Geometric Shapes: U+25A0–U+25FF - Extended Shapes: U+1F780–U+1F7FF

docs.title: ➗ Math Symbols
docs.text: Ranges: - Math Operators: U+2200–U+22FF - Misc. Math A: U+27C0–U+27EF - Misc. Math B: U+2980–U+29FF

docs.title: 🎭 Pictographs & Emoticons
docs.text: Includes: - Misc Symbols & Pictographs: U+1F300–U+1F5FF - Emoticons: U+1F600–U+1F64F - Transport: U+1F680–U+1F6FF - Supplemental: U+1F900–U+1F9FF - Extended-A: U+1FA70–U+1FAFF
